        "type": "object",
        "description": "Outbound webhook payload sent to the partner's `webhook_url`. Delivered as `POST application/json` with headers `X-MRC-Event`, `X-MRC-Signature` (hex HMAC-SHA256 of the raw body using `webhook_secret`), and `X-MRC-Idempotency-Key` (`${order_id}:${event}:${state}`). Receivers MUST de-duplicate on `idempotency_key`.",
